OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1773843069
OL,3,CScottish Parliament votes to reject
OL,4,Cbill to legalise assisted dying
OL,6,FITV News UK Editor Paul Brand breaks
OL,7,Fdown the significance of the vote
OL,8,Fbeing rejected by the Scottish
OL,9,FParliament from outside Holyrood
OL,11,FHolyrood has rejected controversial
OL,12,Flegislation that would have made
OL,13,FScotland the first nation in the UK to
OL,14,Flegalise assisted dying.
OL,16,FScotland's parliament rejected the
OL,17,FAssisted Dying for Terminally Ill
OL,18,FAdults (Scotland) Bill, brought
OL,19,Fforward by Liberal Democrat MSP Liam
OL,20,FMcArthur, by 57 to 69 on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1773843069
OL,3,CScottish Parliament votes to reject
OL,4,Cbill to legalise assisted dying
OL,6,FHealth Secretary Neil Gray announced
OL,7,Fearlier in the day that he would
OL,8,Fabstain from the vote after spending a
OL,9,Fnight in hospital.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV News UK Editor Paul
OL,12,FBrand following the vote, McArthur
OL,13,Fsaid he was "devastated" and that he
OL,14,Fwas "desperate" to get the bill over
OL,15,Fthe line for the families of "dying
OL,16,FScots".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1773843069
OL,3,CScottish Parliament votes to reject
OL,4,Cbill to legalise assisted dying
OL,6,FHe said: "Well, I think it was always
OL,7,Finevitable. I thought this for some
OL,8,Ftime now, that the closer you get to
OL,9,Fthat final vote, the enormity, the
OL,10,Fsignificance of what MSPs will be
OL,11,Fasked to do weighs more and more
OL,12,Fheavily."
OL,14,FHe added: "I think the sadness is that
OL,15,Fdoing nothing has serious consequences
OL,16,Fof leaving those dying Scots who
OL,17,Fdesperately need more choice and more
OL,18,Fcontrol, more vulnerable, isolated,
OL,19,Fand at risk. It's prevented us from
OL,20,Fbeing able to put in place safeguards
OL,21,Fthat just aren't there."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1773843069
OL,3,CScottish Parliament votes to reject
OL,4,Cbill to legalise assisted dying
OL,6,FThe decision came after opponents of
OL,7,Fthe Bill raised concerns about the
OL,8,Fimpact the legislation could have on
OL,9,Fvulnerable and disabled people, while
OL,10,Fothers raised concerns about a lack of
OL,11,Fsafeguards for medical professionals
OL,12,Fopting out of the process.
OL,14,FMSPs made changes to the Bill in four
OL,15,Flengthy sessions at Holyrood last
OL,16,Fweek, with a total of 175 changes to
OL,17,Fthe legislation agreed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1773843069
OL,3,CScottish Parliament votes to reject
OL,4,Cbill to legalise assisted dying
OL,6,FThis was the third time MSPs have
OL,7,Fconsidered legislation on assisted
OL,8,Fdying, with two previous attempts
OL,9,Fhaving failed at their first vote.
OL,11,FMcArthur had earlier insisted the
OL,12,Fproposals would be "the toughest and
OL,13,Fmost comprehensively safeguarded
OL,14,Fassisted dying Bill in the world".
OL,16,FHe met with campaigners who backed a
OL,17,Fchange in the law outside of Holyrood
OL,18,Fon Tuesday ahead of the vote.
OL,26,@tD@TOUvD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
