PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1773843069
OL,3,CScottish Parliament votes to reject
OL,4,Cbill to legalise assisted dying
OL,6,FOpponents of the legislation, who fear
OL,7,Fthe impact of assisted dying on the
OL,8,Fdisabled and other vulnerable groups,
OL,9,Falso gathered outside the Scottish
OL,10,FParliament in advance of the vote.
OL,12,FHolyrood's vote on assisted dying
OL,13,Fcomes as Jersey passed legislation to
OL,14,Flegalise assisted dying for some
OL,15,Fterminally ill residents last month.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
