FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1773843069
OL,3,CScottish Parliament votes to reject
OL,4,Cbill to legalise assisted dying
OL,6,FThey have raised concerns about the
OL,7,Fslow progress of the Terminally Ill
OL,8,FAdults (End of Life) Bill through the
OL,9,FHouse of Lords, with only half of the
OL,10,F1,200 amendments up for consideration
OL,11,Fhaving been debated after 11 days of
OL,12,Fscrutiny.
OL,14,FOpponents of the Bill have been
OL,15,Faccused of trying to "talk out" the
OL,16,FBill as it makes its way through the
OL,17,FLords.
OL,26,@wD@VOUwD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
