OL,3,CScottish Parliament votes to reject
OL,4,Cbill to legalise assisted dying
OL,6,FThe government's stated position on
OL,7,Fthe Assisted Dying Bill is that it
OL,8,Fwill remain neutral, as changing the
OL,9,Flaw should be a matter of individual
OL,10,Fconscience for parliamentarians.
